nodes.text: During the Clone Wars, a Zygerrian female was allied with the Frangawl Cult hailing from the planet Bardotta. The Zygerrian was present on the planet Zardossa Stix when members of the cult had kidnapped the Bardottan Queen Julia and had taken her there. The Zygerrian tried to stall Jedi Master Mace Windu and Gungan Representative Jar Jar Binks from saving Julia.
